  1. You should notice there are a lot of 0s. That is a place where the employment title was left blank. Replace those 0s with NA. Show the summary of that variable below. Should we do this with any 0 values in a variable? Why or why not? Why did we do that here?

Not every variable should be replaced with NA if there are a lot of zeros. Doing this with every variable would cause issues with variables that make sense to have 0 values in them. When doing it with employee title, no one can have a title of 0 characters hense why it makes sense to remove the zeros and replace them with NA values.
